        "ai_gen_block_81e2226_6rNWFD": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_81e2226",
          "settings": {
            "max_content_width": 1000,
            "tab_1_enabled": true,
            "tab_1_title": "Story（产品设计）",
            "tab_1_content": "<p><strong>板块作用：这里用于告知用户产品的设计概念</strong></p><p><strong>HASUKI Black Ops — Mountain Warfare Special Operative</strong></p><p>The SA03 \"Sierra Phantom\" brings alpine combat to your 1/12 scale collection. <br/><br/>Clad in cold-weather tactical gear with an L7 jacket, snow camouflage suit, and full mountaineering kit including ice axes, crampons, and climbing ropes, this 17cm action figure is ready for high-altitude missions. The highly articulated body supports dynamic posing — from rappelling stances to precision rifle handling.<br/><br/>Every detail is meticulously reproduced: the SCAR-H battle rifle with removable suppressor and optical sight, the MPU5 radio system for comms realism, and the 375BK combat knife with sheath. With 10 interchangeable hands, you can configure this operator for any tactical scenario.<br/><br/>Whether displayed solo or paired with other Black Ops series figures, the Sierra Phantom delivers museum-grade detail at an accessible price point. A must-have for military 1/12 collectors and HASUKI enthusiasts alike.</p>",
            "tab_2_enabled": true,
            "tab_2_title": "What's Included(包含什么)",
            "tab_2_content": "<p>该部分作用：告知产品配件<br/>功能调整：这里需要可以插入图片，文案需要可以双列</p><h3>Standard Set Includes</h3><ul><li>L7 Cold Weather Jacket & Pants ×1</li><li>Snow Camouflage Suit ×1</li><li>Chest Rig ×1</li><li>Rifle Sling ×1</li><li>Rappelling Harness ×1</li><li>Climbing Rope Sleeves ×2</li><li>Main Climbing Rope ×1</li><li>Morale Patches ×3</li><li>Tactical Backpack ×1</li></ul><h3>Pre-Order Bonus Items</h3><p>Camouflage Backpack Cover ×1</p><p>Head Sculpt ×1</p><p>Next-Generation Articulated Body ×1</p><p>Interchangeable Hands ×10</p><p>Mountaineering Boots ×1 Pair</p><p>MPU5 Tactical Radio System ×1</p><p>375BK Combat Knife with Sheath ×1</p><p>SCAR-H Rifle with Suppressor ×1</p><p>7.62mm Rifle Magazines ×4</p><p>Optical Scope ×1</p><p>AN/PEQ-15 Laser Module ×1</p><p>Vertical Foregrip ×1</p><p>Drop-Leg Holster ×1</p><p>P226 Pistol (Tan) ×1</p><p>Weapon Light ×1</p><p>9mm Pistol Magazines ×3</p><p>O-Rings ×4</p><p>D-Rings ×4</p><p>Pitons ×3</p><p>Small Nuts ×2</p><p>Large Nuts ×2</p><p>Spring-Loaded Camming Devices ×2</p><p>Ascenders ×2</p><p>Ice Axes ×2</p><p>Quickdraws ×2</p><p>Crampons ×2</p><p>Descender ×1<br/></p><p></p>",
            "tab_3_enabled": true,
            "tab_3_title": "Pre-Order Information（预定信息说明）",
            "tab_3_content": "<p>这里用于写 预售信息  和库存信息；预售商品上架后，注意添加预售标签；</p><p>Limited-Time Pre-Order</p><p>This product is currently in the pre-order stage.</p><p>Pre-Order Period: XXX – XXX</p><p>Special Pre-Order Price: $ XXX</p><p>Future Retail Price: $ XXX</p><p>Orders placed during the pre-order period will receive the exclusive pre-order pricing. After the pre-order closes, the product will be offered at the regular retail price, subject to stock availability.</p><p>Please make sure to place your order before the pre-order deadline.</p>",
            "tab_4_enabled": true,
            "tab_4_title": "Compatibility",
            "tab_4_content": "<p>Compatible With<br/><br/>✓ 1/12 Scale Figures<br/><br/>Recommended Bodies<br/><br/>✓ Damtoys<br/>✓ VeryCool<br/>✓ Easy&Simple<br/><br/>Not Compatible<br/><br/>✗ 1/6 Scale<br/>✗ OB24</p>",
            "tab_5_enabled": false,
