            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We process orders Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM (business days only).<br/>· Order processing time: 2-3 business days<br/>· Delivery time: 9-12 business days<br/>· Shipping: Orders are shipped the next business day after processing is completed.<br/>· Orders placed on weekends or public holidays will be processed on the next business day.</p>",
